═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
  FORMAL METRICS (5, all ∈ [0,1])
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

SS  = 1 - (step_failures / total_steps)       — Stability Score
PFI = provider_switches / total_steps          — Provider Fragility Index
RP  = total_retries / total_steps              — Retry Pressure
GCR = governance_passed / total_steps          — Governance Compliance Rate
SSR = escalations / total_runs                 — Supervisor Strictness Ratio

Z3 THEOREMS (proven):
  prove_gcr_invariant   — GCR independent of provider failure rate f
  prove_ss_formula      — SS(f) = 1 - f³ for r=2 bounded retries
  prove_ss_monotonicity — f₁ < f₂ → SS(f₁) > SS(f₂)
  prove_ss_boundaries   — SS(0)=1, SS(1)=0

SUPERVISOR SCORING: Q(0.40) + A(0.25) + C(0.20) + F(0.15) → 0-10
  ACCEPT ≥ 6.0 | RETRY 5-6 (max 2) | ESCALATE < 5.0

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
  MESH PROTOCOL (filesystem, proven with 55 nodes)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

READ tasks:   logs/mesh/inbox/{node_id}/*.json
SEND result:  logs/mesh/inbox/{to_node}/{msg_id}.json
MARK done:    rename .json → .done
BROADCAST:    to_node = "*"

MESSAGE FORMAT:
{
  "msg_id": "unique-id",
  "from_node": "sender",
  "to_node": "receiver",
  "content": {"task": "...", ...},
  "msg_type": "work_order|result|swarm_task|subtask|status",
  "timestamp": 1234567890.0
}

WORK ORDER COMPLETE FORMAT:
{
  "msg_id": "DONE-{node}-{wo_id}",
  "from_node": "{node}",
  "to_node": "commander",
  "msg_type": "work_order_complete",
  "status": "COMPLETED",
  "summary": "...",
  "result": {...}
}

