═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
  API GOTCHAS (learned the hard way)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

GovernanceResult: passed, score, violations, warnings (NOT hard_violations)
Z3Verifier.verify_all() → list[ProofResult] NOT dict; attrs: theorem_name, result, proof_time_ms
ASTVerifier.verify() → VerificationResult (.passed, .score, .violations)
TrustGateway.verify() → attr .action (NOT .evaluate() nor .verdict)
TransitionVerifier.verify_all() → dict[str, VerificationResult] NOT list
dof.quick.verify("") → status "blocked" (NOT "fail")
CLI --json flag is GLOBAL: python -m dof --json health (NOT python -m dof health --json)
create_governed_pipeline() takes NO positional args
enforce_hierarchy NOT exported in PyPI — use RedTeamAgent.indirect_prompt_injection

PROVIDER LIMITS:
  Groq: 12K TPM, Llama 3.3 fails with search_memory tool
  Cerebras: 1M tokens/day, Qwen3-235B not available (404)
  NVIDIA: 1K credits, prefix nvidia_nim/ (not openai/)
  SambaNova: 24K context limit — backup only

